quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,Toot gaye Abu Lahab ke haath aur na-murad ho gaya woh
  111,2,Uska maal aur jo kuch us ne kamaya woh uske kisi kaam na aaya
  111,3,Zaroor woh shola zan Aag mei dala jayega
  111,4,Aur (us ke saath) us ki joru(wife) bhi lagai bujhai karne wali
  111,5,Us ki gardan(neck) mein moonj ki rassi hogi